data.description: Welcome to Your New Home! Step into a warm and inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch-style residence that promises the perfect blend of comfort and style. Whether you're seeking space for your family or guests, this home offers three generously sized bedrooms, ensuring everyone's comfort.  This home has the converted garage, now transformed into a fantastic media room. It's a versatile space that's ideal for movie nights, game days, or simply as a cozy spot to unwind with loved ones. You'll find endless possibilities for creating unforgettable moments here. With two full bathrooms, the morning rush will be a thing of the past.  And with an extended driveway, parking multiple vehicles will be a breeze, making hosting gatherings a cinch.  The one-story ranch-style layout ensures accessibility and a comfortable flow throughout the home. No more climbing stairs – everything you need is easily accessible on a single level. Nestled in a delightful neighborhood, this house not only offers a comfortable living space but also a sense of community. Enjoy the peaceful surroundings and the friendly atmosphere that comes with it.  This home is much more than just a house; it's a place where you can create lasting memories with your loved ones. Whether you're relaxing in the spacious living area, preparing delicious meals in the kitchen, or enjoying your favorite movies in the media room, you'll feel right at home. Don't wait too long; homes with such features tend to sell quickly. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and make this dream home yours!
